Uses of Interface
sudokuGame.Variable

    • Uses of Variable in sudokuGame

      Classes in sudokuGame that implement Variable 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  BoardIndividual
      BoardIndividual is representing the player that trying to solve the sudoku board, this class is extend Individual abstract class and implement the abstract method evaluate that call play method that will try to solve the sudoku board according to the tree-based GP, and return the fitness of the BoardIndividual.
      class  Individual
      Individual abstract class is representing one player (individual), set of genes, that trying to solve the gaven sudoku board, the program will end if one individual success to solve the sudoku board, and if NO one success to solve the sudoku then we use evolutionary algorithm (next generation) method to create new generation of individuals that trying to solve the sudoku.
